```zsh
while IFS=':' read -r user _ _ _ _ _ shell; do
    echo "$user $shell"
done < /etc/passwd
```

* 利用 `read` 的字段拆分
* `_` 表示“丢弃字段”
* `/etc/passwd` 固定 7 列

```zsh
while read -r line; do
    fields=("${(s/:/)line}")
    echo "${fields[1]} ${fields[-1]}"
done < /etc/passwd
```